                Unlimited recordings
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
